result.notes: Sublittoral MNCR classification map of the Wash, and the Lincolnshire and north Norfolk coasts. This survey was one of three trial areas chosen for the Broadscale Mapping Project. The methodology relies on acoustic ground discrimination system (AGDS) based on a single beam echo sounder
result.title: Broadscale remote survey and mapping of the sublittoral habitats and biota of the Wash, and the Lincolnshire and the north Norfolk coasts - MNCR classification
